SQL databases
Example: MySQL, PostgreSQL

4я╕ПтГг Object-Oriented Model

Data stored as objects
OOP concept ржПрж░ ржорждрзЛ

5я╕ПтГг Document Model (NoSQL)

JSON-like documents
Example: MongoDB, Firestore

6я╕ПтГг KeyтАУValue Model
key тЖТ value
Very fast
Example: Redis

7я╕ПтГг Columnar Model

Column-wise storage
Big Data use
Example: Cassandra, HBase

8я╕ПтГг Graph Model

Nodes + Relationships
Social networks-type
